    </content>
    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>SERI News, February / March 17</title>
      <lead>Information from the State Secretariat for Education, Research and Innovation SERI: VPET 2030 – Feedback from the online community / Horizon 2020 – an appraisal of the current situation / Research institutions of national importance / ...</lead>
      <text link="no">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VPET 2030 – Feedback from the online community&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Digitisation as both an opportunity and risk for the Swiss VPET system&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bilingual VET programme in commerce&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;‘Two vocational qualifications and three years of work experience are non-negligible assets for entry into the labour market’&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;International university ranking lists&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Strong demand for information about universities&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Research institutions of national importance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Part-funding of research institutions boosts research and innovation in Switzerland long term&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Horizon 2020 – an appraisal of the current situation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Continuing a long tradition of cooperation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;International relations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;A busy year for bilateral relations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Astronaut Thomas Pesquet in space&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;“Hello, is that the International Space Station? Sion calling!”&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</text>
